OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777856582
OL,3,CUK to enter talks on joining EU's #78
OL,4,Cbillion loan for Ukraine
OL,6,FThe UK intends to start talks to join
OL,7,Fthe European Union's 90 billion euro
OL,8,F(#78 billion) loan for Ukraine, as the
OL,9,FGovernment seeks to bolster support
OL,10,Ffor Kyiv and deepen defence ties with
OL,11,Fthe bloc.
OL,13,FSir Keir Starmer will tell leaders at
OL,14,Fa European gathering in Armenia's
OL,15,Fcapital Yerevan on Monday that Britain
OL,16,Fwants to work more closely with them
OL,17,Fto ensure Ukraine gets the military
OL,18,Fequipment it needs to continue its
OL,19,Ffightback against Russia's invasion.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
