OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777856582
OL,3,CUK to enter talks on joining EU's #78
OL,4,Cbillion loan for Ukraine
OL,6,FThe bid to participate in the loan
OL,7,Fscheme ` recently approved by the EU
OL,8,Fafter Viktor Orban's defeat in
OL,9,FHungarian elections ended a long-
OL,10,Frunning impasse ` is part of the Prime
OL,11,FMinister's reset with Brussels.
OL,13,FSir Keir called for the UK and EU to
OL,14,F"go further and faster on defence" co-
OL,15,Foperation before his visit to the
OL,16,FEuropean Political Community summit
OL,17,F(EPC) in Armenia, only the second by a
OL,18,FBritish leader to the Caucasus country
OL,19,Fand the first in more than 25 years.
OL,26,@vD@AOUvD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777856582
OL,3,CUK to enter talks on joining EU's #78
OL,4,Cbillion loan for Ukraine
OL,6,FHe also noted access to the initiative
OL,7,Fcould create opportunities for British
OL,8,Fdefence firms to compete for contracts
OL,9,Funder the scheme.
OL,11,FThe UK will also slap further
OL,12,Fsanctions on Russian companies to
OL,13,Fdisrupt military supply chains later
OL,14,Fthis week, according to Downing Street.
OL,16,FThe Prime Minister said: "When the UK
OL,17,Fand the European Union work together,
OL,18,Fwe all reap the benefits ` and in
OL,19,Fthese volatile times we need to go
OL,20,Ffurther and faster on defence to keep
OL,21,Fpeople safe.
OL,26,@xD@ZOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777856582
OL,3,CUK to enter talks on joining EU's #78
OL,4,Cbillion loan for Ukraine
OL,6,F"That is why we are beginning
OL,7,Fnegotiations with the EU to ensure
OL,8,FUkraine gets the equipment it needs to
OL,9,Fdefend its freedom, while driving
OL,10,Fopportunities for British industry to
OL,11,Fplay its full part.
OL,13,F"I will always act in our national
OL,14,Finterest: protecting our security,
OL,15,Fsupporting our allies, and delivering
OL,16,Fjobs and stability at home."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUxD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
