FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777856582
OL,3,CUK to enter talks on joining EU's #78
OL,4,Cbillion loan for Ukraine
OL,6,FSir Keir has indicated he wants to
OL,7,Fwork more closely with the EU on
OL,8,Fdefence, even after talks aimed at the
OL,9,FUK potentially joining Brussels' 150
OL,10,Fbillion euro (#130 billion) Security
OL,11,FAction for Europe rearmament fund
OL,12,Fbroke down at the end of last year as
OL,13,Fthe price for entry was considered too
OL,14,Fhigh.
OL,16,FBefore his Armenia trip, the Labour
OL,17,Fleader wrote in The Observer that
OL,18,FBrexit had "damaged our economy" and
OL,19,Fthat strengthening economic links with
OL,20,Fthe continent was key to recovery.
OL,26,@zD@LOUzD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
