FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777856582
OL,3,CUK to enter talks on joining EU's #78
OL,4,Cbillion loan for Ukraine
OL,6,FThe UK and EU, which will hold another
OL,7,Fjoint summit this summer, will
OL,8,Fnegotiate the parameters of access to
OL,9,Fthe bloc's loan for Ukraine in the
OL,10,Fcoming weeks, No 10 said.
OL,12,FThe EU last month approved the
OL,13,Ffinancial boost, vital to keep Ukraine
OL,14,Fafloat for the next two years, after
OL,15,FHungary lifted its veto.
OL,17,FSir Keir is expected to hold meetings
OL,18,Fwith some of his European counterparts
OL,19,Fin the margins of the EPC.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777856582
OL,3,CUK to enter talks on joining EU's #78
OL,4,Cbillion loan for Ukraine
OL,6,FWhen the Prime Minister met Volodymyr
OL,7,FZelensky in Yerevan on Sunday, the
OL,8,FUkrainian president thanked the King
OL,9,Ffor his "strong words" on the defence
OL,10,Fof Ukraine during his state visit to
OL,11,Fthe United States, for UK sanctions
OL,12,Fagainst Russia and efforts to counter
OL,13,Fthe shadow fleet.
OL,15,FThe meeting of the EPC, formed in 2022
OL,16,Fafter Moscow's full-scale invasion of
OL,17,FUkraine, comes as US President Donald
OL,18,FTrump has shifted his attention from
OL,19,Fthat conflict to the one in the Middle
OL,20,FEast.
OL,26,@qD@IOUqD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
